  <section class="section" aria-labelledby="testi-kl-h">
    <div class="inner" style="max-width:760px;">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <span class="tag tag-dim" style="margin-bottom:16px;display:inline-flex;">Verified result</span>
        <h2 id="testi-kl-h">From a Store That Made the Switch</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="testi-grid" style="grid-template-columns:1fr;">
        <div class="tc featured">
          <div class="tc-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p class="tc-quote">"We were paying Klaviyo $320/month. Systeme.io does everything we actually used — welcome sequences, abandoned cart, post-purchase — for zero dollars. The migration took 25 minutes. I can't believe we waited so long to switch."</p>
          <div class="tc-name">Priya M.</div>
          <div class="tc-store">DTC Skincare Brand (~£45k/mo GMV) · Switched from Klaviyo $320/mo</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="section-alt" id="faq" aria-labelledby="faq-h" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage">
    <div class="inner-sm">
      <div class="sec-head">
        <span class="tag tag-dim" style="margin-bottom:16px;display:inline-flex;">FAQ</span>
        <h2 id="faq-h">Klaviyo vs Systeme.io — Common Questions</h2>
      </div>
